                            "text": "<ul class=\"stat-block-2\"><li>A <i>transmute rock to mud </i>spell slows a fossil golem (as the <i>slow</i> spell) for 2d6 rounds, with no saving throw.</li>\n<li>A <i>stone to flesh</i> spell negates its damage reduction and petrification ability for 1 round.</li></ul>"
